title: Retard Strength Official Discography (2014-2015)
description:
RETARD STRENGTH OFFICIAL 2014-2015 DISCOGRAPHY
Contains the first to-date albums of the Retard Strength duo collaborative. 
Plus two unreleased never-before-heard EPs that sprung from the deadly battle of
the jews and their copyright. All tracks have been remastered by Mac B himself, with the vintage ones still in tact on their Youtube channel.


Albums
The Circus Van [9 Tracks, 2014 *REMASTERED]

Goblin Radio [4 Tracks, 2014 *REMASTERED]

Skittish [21 Tracks, 2014 *REMASTERED]

Greenies EP [2 Tracks, 2015 Original *BONUS EP]

Copyright Embassy Deadly Battle EP [2 Tracks, 2015 Original *BONUS EP]

Arbor Interior [22 Tracks, 2015 Original, LATEST RELEASE, featuring Moon Man of YTMND Fame]


Short autobiograph: A fucked up producer (Mac B) and a truly-southern stoner guitarist (Danny Downs) both stationed in Buttphuq, Alabama get together and make the best music since Tenacious D. Proud holders of such classics as 
-Niggers Beware
-HivBola
-Give Me Admin
-White American Earth-God
-Soiled Man
and -Christ Love,
the two dong-tanglers make it not their job, but their /duty/ to sexually exploit every orifice in your body via their music.


Genres: Industrial, Clown Funk, Folk, Country, Singer/Songwriter, Rape Rap, Amoral Ballad, Cosmic Funk, Hip Hop, and Lo-Fi Acid Jazz.

Keep seedin'!

--- Mac B
